  "title": "Sales Engineer (Semicon/Automation)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of promoting sales of electronics assembly products and solutionsto achieve sales targets</li>\n  <li>Responsible for working with customers and principals in sales activities like presentation, quotation, specification confirmation, negotiation, commissioning and acceptance</li>\n  <li>In charge of building and maintaining good rapport with customers, principals and vendors</li>\n  <li>Responsible in conducting evaluation for system, parts and materials with customers</li>\n  <li>Responsible for developing account development strategies to increase sales from new and existing customers</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Degree in Mechanical/ Electrical/ Electronics Engineering</li>\n  <li>Min 1 years technical sales experience in Electronics and Semiconductor industries</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid class 3 license</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong>or call <strong>+(65) 6513 5697</strong> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
